1. *Farma* je bila prepuna životinja. (*Farma* - The farm was full of animals.)
2. Danas ćemo posetiti *farmu* u selu. (Today we will visit a *farm* in the village.)
3. *Farmaš* je bio veoma uspešan u svom poslu. (*Farmaš* - The farmer was very successful in his job.)
4. Ovde je posađena nova *farmeraj* koja će se brzo razvijati. (*Farmeraj* - New farmland has been planted here, which will quickly develop.)
5. Pre nego što krenemo, moramo da pripremimo *farmericu* i ostale poljoprivredne alate. (*Farmerica* - Before we start, we need to prepare the tractor and other agricultural tools.)
6. *Farmer* je hranio stoku pre nego što je otišao na spavanje. (*Farmer* - The farmer fed the livestock before he went to sleep.)
7. Ovaj kraj je poznat po *farmanju* i proizvodnji sira. (*Farmanje* - This area is known for farming and cheese production.)
8. Povrće koje raste na *farmama* obično ima bolji ukus od onog koje se prodaje u supermarketima. (*Farme* - Vegetables that grow on farms usually taste better than those sold in supermarkets.)